sentence: what's the difference between fare code q and fare code b
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.booking_class||'"', v0.rank, '"'||v0.class_description||'"' FROM class_of_service v0 
WHERE ((v0.booking_class = 'Q') OR (v0.booking_class = 'B'));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT CLASS_OF_SERVICE.BOOKING_CLASS , CLASS_OF_SERVICE.RANK , CLASS_OF_SERVICE.CLASS_DESCRIPTION FROM CLASS_OF_SERVICE WHERE ( CLASS_OF_SERVICE.BOOKING_CLASS = ' Q ' OR CLASS_OF_SERVICE.BOOKING_CLASS = ' B ' ) ) ;
